title: Mortgage Debt Outstanding by Type of Holder: Major Financial Institutions: Depository Institutions (DISCONTINUED)
notes:
The Mortgage Debt Outstanding table is no longer being updated as of March 2020. Many of the series that were published in this table can be found in the Z1 Financial Accounts of the United States release. The Z1 equivalent of this series is the sum of BOGZ1FL763065005Q (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BOGZ1FL763065005Q), BOGZ1FL753065005Q (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BOGZ1FL753065005Q) and BOGZ1FL763065003Q (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BOGZ1FL763065005Q).

For further information, please refer to the Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System's Mortgage Debt Outstanding (http://www.federalreserve.gov/econresdata/releases/mortoutstand/current.htm).
